<P><PB N="80" REF="90">
They followed his advice; and before
day break on the twentieth of December,
near &s;even months after their arrival in the
I&s;le of Skie, they quitted it; and landing
&s;afely on the coa&s;t of Scotland, they pro|ceeded
with very great fatigue, though
