<P><PB N="224" REF="234">
Another deep &s;igh was all the lady's an|&s;wer
to this information: but Lord Ca&s;tle|north
cried&mdash;"I am &s;orry to hear you &s;ay
&s;o, George&mdash;very &s;orry. I did hope that
we might have all returned together as &s;oon
