<P>"The world!" exclaimed the lady.
"Lord ble&s;s me, what &s;ignifies the opinion
of the world. The world cannot &s;ee as I
do into all their feelings. There's your
mo&s;t excellent uncle, as worthy a man as
ever exi&s;ted, &s;inking, poor good dear
