&s;he, "is it thus we meet again after &s;uch
<PB N="262" REF="272">
a parting? Is this the end of all your a&s;|&s;urances,
that you would ever be my friend?
that you would learn to con&s;ider me as your
&s;i&s;ter if we were indeed related? alas! is it
thus then you throw me off entirely, and
&s;eem &s;orry to remember that you ever &s;aw
